{"tid":946154,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[25仔背叛爺爺下場] 韋舒亞提早收咧？","createTime":"2018-12-18T10:54:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-19T06:16:44.000Z","uid":28435,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5edca4d86fc9fa2f29f352efbd9a7252126bc125","tid":946154,"uid":28435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T10:54:52.000Z","msg":"雖然韋斯咸近日錄得4連勝可喜可賀，但今季由阿仙奴加盟的中場韋舒亞，卻可能要提早收咧。<br />\n<br />\n韋舒亞（Jack Wilshere）自9月接受左腳足踝手術後，至今只上陣一場僅5分鐘，以為可以慢慢操起狀態，豈料26歲的韋舒亞又在最近的訓練中弄傷右足踝，英國《太陽報》引述韋斯咸內部人士表示，假如韋舒亞再多休息幾周還是沒有起色的話，或要再接受手術，今季餘下賽季亦要報銷。<br />\n<br />\n早前韋斯咸領隊柏歷堅尼已經表示，不知道韋舒亞何時才能夠復出。<br />\n<br />\n鎚仔幫本身已有翼鋒耶莫蘭高與中場蘭仙尼傷出，今季應難以見到二人上陣，守將雲斯頓列特亦要再過一段時間才能復出，好在憑著將士用命球隊近日取得4連捷，排在聯賽榜第9位。<br />\n<br />\n同張九零同一下場 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2621063989719955c505aaca9383b473112abfe","tid":946154,"uid":26959,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T12:00:46.000Z","msg":"佢有邊季唔洗提早收咧<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3616d11d97ab1817ca9e25038542ec02b561a687","tid":946154,"uid":15830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T16:06:33.000Z","msg":"英撚唯一play maker又收咧<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6574bd6352886df165400d169f1ceba5f70f4b8","tid":946154,"uid":30476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T16:07:32.000Z","msg":"佢邊有背叛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01e90a8f3781e1b678c123890ec1786a89b81ef0","tid":946154,"uid":581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T16:20:11.000Z","msg":"唔背叛佢都成日傷架啦"},{"pid":"81dddf6a0c262079a88619266c9891edb106531e","tid":946154,"uid":67